<script type="text/javascript">
(function (w,c,g,p){
    if (typeof(w["yaCounter"+c])=='undefined'){
       /*console.log("yaCounter"+c+" is not defined yet");*/
       (w['_yac']=w['_yac']||[]).push({
        id:c,
        values: {
         func:'reachGoal',
         goal:g,
         param:('undefined'==typeof(p))?'':p
        }
       });
    } else {
        try {
            w["yaCounter"+c].reachGoal(g,p);
        } catch(e) {};
    }
})(window,{{YM-ID}},{{yandexGoal}},{{yandexParams}});
</script>

<script>
(function(w,c){
  /*console.log(typeof(w['_yac']));*/
  if ( 'undefined' != typeof(w['_yac']) ){
   /*console.log(w['_yac']);*/
   for (var i in w['_yac']){
        try {
               var ob = w['_yac'][i];
               /*console.log(ob);*/
               /*console.log(ob.values.func);*/
               switch (ob.values.func){
                 case 'reachGoal': 
                      w["yaCounter"+ob.id].reachGoal(ob.values.goal,ob.values.param);
                      break;
                 default : console.log(ob);
               }
        } catch(e) {};
   }
   var undef;
   w['_yac'] = undef;
  }
})(window, {{YM-ID}});
</script>
